<TEXT>Have owned this auto for almost two years - no problems, oil changes only. I will buy a new one when the 2010 models come out. You can't buy a better made auto for the price. (a friend bought an Accord, paid more and got less - no comparison on handling)</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Everything!</FAVORITE>
