We brought the 2007 Accord to the Nissan dealership to compare them side by side, and the Nissan won, hands down. Many more features, better looks, more comfort. Wife loved the car. If Momma's happy...</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>The CVT id really cool. Bluetooth. HID is important in the boonies! Seats are great. Lots of room in back for the two kids. Smooth ride. Easy to pass others. Doing 100 before you know it. This is not the 350Z, though. If you want a race car, buy one. This is a great sedan. Leather is great.</FAVORITE>
